Package cpsc3720.contactclient

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AttackLogModel  
    ContactClient
    Launches the initial window.
    GameListModel
    Represents the set of games to be displayed in the JoinGameFrame window.
    GhostText
    This class renders the text in the text boxes on the login screen.
    JoinGameFrame
    JoinGameFrame is used to select a game instance from the server.
    LoginFrame
    The initial JFrame of the program, this window gathers server location data and user data to log in to the game.
    MainGameScreen
    MainGameScreen generates the JFrame window which is used to interact with the game state.
    PopupListener
    Used to generate the popup for the alert level button.
    SectorTableModel
    Sector table model is used to display the game's sector data in a JTable on MainGameScreen
    UniverseTableModel
    Responsible for the Universe JTable data model on MainGameScreen.
